In a cocktail shaker, combine 1/2 cup BACARDI(R) Mixers Strawberry Daiquiri Mix, 1/8 cup blueberries, about 12 medium-large sage leaves, and muddle. Add remaining ingredients except for garnishes, ice, and shake vigorously for about 30 seconds. Strain into a chilled cocktail or martini glass. Garnish with 3 blueberries and sage leaf on a cocktail pick.